        <p data-role="text">The Jig&#xAD;ger &amp; Pony Group launched Pony last month, a pre&#xAD;mium bot&#xAD;tled cock&#xAD;tail brand that takes the bar to the home. They are avail&#xAD;able in el&#xAD;e&#xAD;gant mini (200ml) and stan&#xAD;dard&#xD;&#xA;(500ml) bot&#xAD;tles.</p>
